        {
            "id": 6327936,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大跌2%，報8154.31點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間31日12:20，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>下跌166.08點（或2%），暫報8154.31點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+3.29%</li><li>近 1 月：+15.91%</li><li>近 3 月：+13.54%</li><li>近 6 月：+44.96%</li><li>今年以來：+17.47%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以科磊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KLAC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KLAC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KLAC-US</a>)領跌。科磊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:KLAC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/KLAC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">KLAC-US</a>)下跌12.77%；超微半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMD-US</a>)下跌4.46%；Onto Innovation Inc.(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)下跌3.87%；格羅方德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GFS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GFS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GFS-US</a>)下跌3.59%；英特格(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ENTG:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ENTG\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ENTG-US</a>)下跌3.53%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對穩健，博通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVGO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVGO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVGO-US</a>)上漲1.02%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)上漲0.74%；高通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>)上漲0.11%；美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)上漲0.02%。</p></section></main>",
